---
title: Creamy Chicken, Bacon and Mushroom Pie  with Potato Topping and Roasted Carrots
description: This Creamy Chicken, Bacon and Mushroom Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
